<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='753000' id='t-753000'>the opportunities in various other sectors are enormous.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:49
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='758000' id='t-758000'>We have opportunities in agriculture, like I said.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='761000' id='t-761000'>We have opportunities in solid minerals. We have a lot of minerals</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='765000' id='t-765000'>that no one has even invested in or explored. And we realized</span>
