</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='803000' id='t-803000'>So, huge things in construction, real estate,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='806000' id='t-806000'>mortgage markets. Financial services:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='809000' id='t-809000'>we had 89 banks. Too many not doing their real business.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='813000' id='t-813000'>We consolidated them from 89 to 25 banks by requiring</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='817000' id='t-817000'>that they increase their capital -- share capital.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='822000' id='t-822000'>And it went from about 25 million dollars to 150 million dollars.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='827000' id='t-827000'>The banks -- these banks are now consolidated, and that strengthening</span>
