<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='843000' id='t-843000'>And I can go on. Dollars, on and on, into the system.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:17
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='846000' id='t-846000'>We are doing the same with the insurance sector.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='848000' id='t-848000'>So in financial services, a great deal of opportunity.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='851000' id='t-851000'>In tourism, in many African countries, a great opportunity.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='857000' id='t-857000'>And that's what many people know East Africa for:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='861000' id='t-861000'>the wildlife, the elephants, and so on.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='864000' id='t-864000'>But managing the tourism market in a way</span>
