</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:41
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='870000' id='t-870000'>So what am I trying to say? I'm trying to tell you</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='873000' id='t-873000'>that there's a new wave on the continent.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='876000' id='t-876000'>A new wave of openness and democratization in which, since 2000,</span>
