<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='926000' id='t-926000'>it looks like the entire continent is affected.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='929000' id='t-929000'>But you should know that this continent is not --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='932000' id='t-932000'>is a continent of many countries, not one country.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='938000' id='t-938000'>And if we are down to three or four conflicts,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='940000' id='t-940000'>it means that there are plenty of opportunities to invest</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='943000' id='t-943000'>in stable, growing, exciting economies</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='950000' id='t-950000'>where there's plenty of opportunity.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='954000' id='t-954000'>And I want to just make one point about this investment.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='959000' id='t-959000'>The best way to help Africans today</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='962000' id='t-962000'>is to help them to stand on their own feet.</span>
