<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='997000' id='t-997000'>isn't that a wonderful opportunity? Isn't that the way to go?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1002000' id='t-1002000'>And I want to say that some of the best people to invest in</span>
